escribe the error, and to identify where it occurred. The information for this is derived from the
nputs error in, error code, and error source, and from an internal error description table. The table de
cribes all errors that can be created by LabVIEW or its associated I/O operations. The handler has provisions to t

r-defined errors. See instruction on the front panel.
